      "rdfs:label": "Do not use a that has high pressure. A water hose that has high pressure can cause some parts to become loose or full of water.",
      "s1000d:dmc": "S1000DBIKE-AAA-D00-0-0-00AA-258B-A",
      "s1000d:text": "Do not use a that has high pressure. A water hose that has high pressure can cause some parts to become loose or full of water."
    },
    {
      "@id": "caution:S1000DBIKE-AAA-D00-0-0-00AA-258B-A:2:do-not-point-the-hose-directly-at-the-hub-or-at-",
